- !<TypeScriptAssetData/703167d6-211e-4641-a513-e57fc96f61e2>
  SvgIcon: ""
  SetupScript:
    code: ""
  Description: |-
    Handles all balloon interactions on the start screen. It detects which balloon the user taps or pinches, hides the remaining balloons, starts the pledge-reading sequence by calling `PledgeReadInOrder.init()`, and later animates the selected balloon before notifying KindnessCounter to record the pledge.  Public APIs  - changeTransform():
    Animates the selected balloon upward then calls KindnessCounter.onBalloonSelected(). This is typically triggered after the voice pledge is captured.
